      "locked": false,
      "text": "HOW : Procedural mode for now , maybe switching in oop in the future\nUSING: Numpy only\nwhat need to be built :  \n-  Implementation of different objective function MSE,CEL\n- Implementation of well known heuristics ( activation functions ) : Relu,Sigmoid,ect\n- Implementing the derivatives of the different activation function\n- Implementing the backward pass engine ! \n\nhaving those tools I will be able to  implement different architectures \nthe backward engine remain the core,critical algorithm to implement ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "HOW : Procedural mode for now , maybe switching in oop in the future\nUSING: Numpy only\nwhat need to be built :  \n-  Implementation of different objective function MSE,CEL\n- Implementation of well known heuristics ( activation functions ) : Relu,Sigmoid,ect\n- Implementing the derivatives of the different activation function\n- Implementing the backward pass engine ! \n\nhaving those tools I will be able to  implement different architectures \nthe backward engine remain the core,critical algorithm to implement ",
